### Create a new client
POST http://localhost:8080/api/clients
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nomUtilisateur": "jdoe",
  "motDePasse": "password123",
  "nom": "John Doe",
  "email": "jdoe@example.com",
  "niveauFidelite": "BASIC"
}

### Get all clients
GET http://localhost:8080/api/clients

### Get client by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/clients/4

### Get client profile (lean, no orders)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/clients/4/profile

### Get client loyalty tier
GET http://localhost:8080/api/clients/4/loyalty-tier

### Get client statistics
GET http://localhost:8080/api/clients/4/stats

### Get client order history
GET http://localhost:8080/api/clients/4/orders

### Update client
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/clients/4
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nomUtilisateur": "jdoe",
  "motDePasse": "newpassword456",
  "nom": "John Doe Updated",
  "email": "jdoe@example.com",
  "niveauFidelite": "PLATINUM"
}

### Delete client
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/clients/4
